by javiereguiluz at 2016-01-19T17:14:35Z

Thank you all for the discussion and the recommendations. At the end I didn't use the Bootstrap Lightbox plugin because I couldn't make it work and because it's officially deprecated. I used http://noelboss.github.io/featherlight/ instead.

This feature is now finished and ready for review. We now have lightbox images everwhere: list, show, edit and new views!

